sentences.english: I need you to get a copy of that new alien alert from the Immigration Department.
sentences.chinese: 我要你从移民局搞一份最新的外侨警报。

sentences.english: Exuse me , my passport has already sent to immigration office to request for work visa ?
sentences.chinese: 请问我的护照有没有送到移民局办理工作签证了？

sentences.english: Tenth, Echina immigration will use the same organization account(Ministry of Foreign Affairs CN) with Ministry of Echina Foreign Affairs.
sentences.chinese: 第十条移民局与外交部合署办公，共用外交部组织号。

sentences.english: They were held up by the immigration authorities.
All aliens must register annually with the Department of Immigration.
sentences.chinese: 所有外侨每年都必须到移民局登记。

sentences.english: The immigration office acts like a login module.
sentences.chinese: 移民局就好像是一个登录模块。

sentences.english: The pair will be questioned by immigration officials and police.
sentences.chinese: 两人即将接受移民局和警方的询问。

sentences.english: Now you've got your boarding pass, you can go through the immigrations and customs controls.

sentences.english: Sam, see that I. N. S. is working with the Red Cross and the Centers for Disease Control.

sentences.english: Please get your passport ready. The immigration officer will check it when you disembark.
sentences.chinese: 请将您的护照准备好，下机后有移民局官员进行检查。

sentences.english: The big Irishman with the Immigration badge looked at him.
sentences.chinese: 那个带着移民局证章的大个子爱尔兰人瞧着他。

sentences.english: Time turns to 2006, NZIS once again brought something fresh.
sentences.chinese: 到了2006年，移民局又有新花样。
